#brand-sidebar
  .title 
    | byAMT
  .misc
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6
      a(href='#')
        img(src='/images/fb.png')
      a(href='#')
        img(src='/images/twitter_2.png')
      a(href='#') Share...
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6.text-right
      a.follow(href='#') Follow
      a(href='#')
        img(src='/images/love-it.png')
    .clearfix
  .brand-info
    | New York-based design studio byAMT creates jewelry, home goods, and furniture that tweak expectations and invite.
  .brand-menu(ng-controller="brandChapterCtrl")
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-md-push-6.col-lg-push-6.text-right
      ul
        li.visible-xs-inline-block.visible-sm-inline-block.visible-md-block.visible-lg-block(ng-repeat="chapter in chapters" ng-class="navClass('{{chapter.name}}')")
          a(href='{{chapter.url}}' style="text-transform: capitalize") {{chapter.name}}
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-md-pull-6.col-lg-pull-6.text-right
      ul(ng-show="navShow('products')")
        li.visible-xs-block.visible-sm-block.visible-md-block.visible-lg-inline-block(ng-class="navOnShow('all')")
          a(href='/brand/chapter/products/all') All
        li.visible-xs-block.visible-sm-block.visible-md-block.visible-lg-inline-block(ng-class="navOnShow('featured')")
          a(href='/brand/chapter/products/featured') Featured
    .clearfix
    